column5: At least they got the windshields clear, good to go.
WOOOOOOOOWWWWWWWWW is that gonna SUCK when the plow goes by   !!!!
Now that the car is dug out, where do they think they are going to go?
Sit inside, start it up to keep warm and break out the Vodka! Probably in a hurry cause they left it in the car?  ccmt, where the heck are those pictures at? Got to tear those pages out of the atlas.
It's the Trans Labrador Highway...here's a link from Snopes.com...these pics were falsely circulated on the web as somewhere in New York....  http://www.snopes.com/photos/natural/oswego.asp
Let them keep it all; we've had enough this year.
